   319тЖТ## Agents
   323тЖТ> Software is changing, and dotenv must change with itтАФthat is why I built [agentic secret storage (AS2)](https://dotenvx.com/as2). Agents run code without humans at terminals, so plaintext `.env` files are the wrong primitive.
   324тЖТ>
      тЖТтАж
